acrobot
Class AcrobotState

java.lang.Object
  environment.AbstractState
      acrobot.AcrobotState
All Implemented Interfaces:
IState, java.io.Serializable
public class AcrobotState
extends AbstractState

As in Sutton and Barto, Acrobot states are defined by two angles and two speeds. But tiling is not used, states are equals if they lie not to far from each other. See the code for method equals

Author:
Francesco De Comite (decomite at lifl.fr)
